headline: West Pharmaceutical Services (WST): Reassessing Valuation After a 20% Share Price Decline
summary: West Pharmaceutical Services (WST) has quietly slipped almost 20% over the past year, even as revenue and net income kept growing. That disconnect between share price and business performance is what makes the stock interesting now. See our latest analysis for West Pharmaceutical Services. Over the past year, West’s share price return has fallen sharply even as its three year total shareholder return remains positive. This suggests momentum has cooled lately as investors reassess growth...
